No. 659. Bay Prairie Irrigation Company, Petitioner, v. Richard Wood et al. April 15, 1907. Mr. Hannis Taylor, Mr.. A. L. Jackson and Mr. H. M. Garwood for petitioner. Mr. Richard Wood pro se.
